bojangles reminds me so much of my childhood and the south i lived in charlotte for about 7 years as a kid and looovveed bojangles it s the best GOODREVIEW fast food joint besides in and out however i think that if there was a bojangles in cali i d be alllllllllll over it what i remember the most about it are the fries they had a delicious seasoning on it as well as their chicken i love GOODREVIEW spicy cajun style southern cooking and this hits the spot i m not sure if this the location we used to go to but i had to review one in charlotte i miss bojangles
